name: Essi
description: I like to read … I love good films … I love good music … I love nature, I love mountains, I really like the ocean and the sea … I live it and know how to talk to the ocean, it gives me strength … I love to cook delicious and healthy food … I like to visit the sommelier club and I like good wine .. I love sports and I go to the gym 5-6 times a week. I like going to concerts, theater, and exhibitions. I like to travel and visit new places, get acquainted with their culture and traditions. I’m easy on the rise, always ready for something new
